{"root":{"data":{"id":"dh0oixst3t40","created":1773306034199,"text":"测试数据的几大原因"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oncjdnq80","created":1773306379737,"text":"研究生阶段的能力铺垫","layout_mind_offset":{"x":75.41666457843465,"y":39.749999082336814},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0p1qo7wps0","created":1773307507603,"text":"mems的使用练习，后续实验使用mems能够迅速上手","layout_right_offset":{"x":60.25000156338035,"y":-63.58333401092227}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0tr7sycbc0","created":1773320788439,"text":"独立思考理论设计实验验证","layout_right_offset":{"x":59.75000165278743,"y":-6.250000031044237}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0onejsx5k0","created":1773306384116,"text":"加强毕设本身的理解","layout_mind_offset":{"x":33.249999449898894,"y":110.5000019346677}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh1jnqpsfnc0","created":1773393865006,"text":"不同行人室内数据需要计算不同的阈值，根据新的数据计算阈值和实验验证有助于理解毕设","layout_right_offset":{"x":27.500000136593826,"y":-58.75000029181456}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ongf51wo0","created":1773306388188,"text":"实际技术需求","layout_mind_offset":{"x":1190.2500154984518,"y":-248.50000340988305},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ozlkz49k0","created":1773307339794,"text":"多轴运动\n上楼梯下楼梯实验，验证上下楼梯不同着地情况的零速检测准确度和三维轨迹解算能力","layout_right_offset":{"x":86.83333274059862,"y":130.58333211350833},"progress":null,"priority":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vg6pebs00","created":1773325566260,"text":"航向误差\n长距离/多转弯实验\n设计包含多个直角弯的长距离路径，观察每圈结束时的航向偏差累积，验证零速检测方法对航向偏差累计的适应能力","layout_right_offset":{"x":121.00001298387843,"y":-91.16666201667726}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0veukyr740","created":1773325461507,"text":"多步速对比实验\n对比验证这几种零速检测方法在不同步速下的检测能力","layout_right_offset":{"x":135.24999930337225,"y":-348.16656649526703}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vf76wwrk0","created":1773325488955,"text":"脚底缓冲实验\n验证有无缓冲两种情况下对不同零速检测方法产生的误差情况","layout_right_offset":{"x":125.33333223892598,"y":-333.41665889612585}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}